<plot>Ice Bears of the Beaufort documents a sophisticated polar bear society threatened by offshore oil &amp; gas development on Alaska's arctic coast. In the US government's process of establishing polar bear "critical habitat" in 2009-10, this film is THE sole documentary record establishing this region as a de facto polar bear sanctuary that deserves protection.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?255621</url></doc>
